49
00:10:42,350 --> 00:10:44,406
{\an8}♫ Bị nhốt trong mây mù ♫

50
00:10:44,430 --> 00:10:47,160
{\an8}♫ Lẩn khuất trong không trung ♫

51
00:10:45,750 --> 00:10:47,050
Đó

52
00:10:48,350 --> 00:10:51,240
